title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 141-3.5 - Resident janitor
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 141-3.5 - Resident janitor

State Regulations
A
resident janitor
is a janitor as
defined above who resides in the building where he or she renders services, or
in another building within a distance of 200 feet therefrom. Notes
